data.title: Rabbit Wine Auto Electric Corkscrew
data.description: The World’s first Automatic Electric Corkscrew; simply place on top of your favorite bottle of wine and let the corkscrew do all the work! Set the corkscrew on top of the bottle and the corkscrew automatically removes and ejects the cork – no buttons necessary. A single charge opens 30+ bottles of wine. This is the easiest corkscrew you’ll ever use – let’s drink to that!

data.title: Rabbit Wine Super Aerator
data.description: Have you ever opened a bottle of highly recommended wine only to be left disappointed? Aerating your wine allows your wine to breathe, enhancing the taste and improving the bouquet. Whether you are serving one glass or the entire bottle, the Rabbit® Super Aerator instantly aerates so you get perfectly aerated wine each time.

data.title: Rabbit Award Winning Push Muddler
data.description:
The Muddler will enhance the flavor of any cocktail. Perfect for Mojitos and Mint Juleps! 
Includes a specially designed head that crushes rather than cuts ingredients to preserve and bring out the best flavors. Pushing down causes the Muddler head to spin, crushing the ingredients with unparalleled speed and ease. Winner of 2015 IHA Innovation Award!

data.title: Rabbit Bar Whiskey Tumbler
data.description: With the Rabbit® Whiskey Glass, the ice is outside your beverage, not in it. The Whiskey Glass will cool your drink down to just above freezing. The silicone base acts as a built-in coaster to prevent condensation from escaping. The silicone sleeve also protects your hands from the chill.
